Package sg.edu.ntu.cz2002.grp3.Controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminController
    The Class AdminController which handles all the functions available to the adminView.
    FileManager
    The Class FileManager handles the connecting to, writing to and reading from the database.
    LoginManager
    The Class LoginManager handles login related functions.
    MyStarsApp
    The Class MyStarsApp starts the application and intitialises the necessary objects.
    NotificationManager
    The Class NotificationManager is an abstraction for the notification packages.
    RecordManager
    The Class RecordManager handles the database records.
    StudentController
    The Class StudentController handles the logic for the options selected in student view, which includes adding, changing, dropping indexes, checking vacancies, and more.
    TimeManager
    The Class TimeManager provides time handling related static functions.
